metadata.name: We're all the same inside?
metadata.description:
I visit a room with a child of two
The lights all hang, glowing different hues
One looks at me, naked, bare
and I realise the rest are all there
hiding in their various masks
all beautiful too.
 
December 2019, Waddesdon Manor, England. 
∆í/2 1/33 3.88 mm ISO186
